A large hawk flies through the desert, the wind through her feathers 
feels wonderful to her but the sand hurts her eyes. She land near the 
area where they picked up translife signs. The hawk seems to half 
transform into a metallic creature with a hawks beak and head, a long 
robotic body, two extended wings flap stirring up even more sand, her 
legs appear to be a robots with bits of feathers on the side, her 
arms are her talons, always extended and ready for action.

"I know you're out there, there's no sense hiding, I've already found 
you."
